00:06:33.940 --> 00:06:38.400
So I know recently, you had,
in the same weekend, Swaziland

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:39.564
Pride and Istanbul Pride.

00:06:39.564 --> 00:06:40.230
MATT BEARD: Yes.

00:06:40.230 --> 00:06:42.271
SPEAKER: All Out was doing
work with both of them

00:06:42.271 --> 00:06:44.880
simultaneously, and there's
pretty different outcomes

00:06:44.880 --> 00:06:46.920
from both, from
