00:18:07.290 --> 00:18:11.060
But we've also started to
collect some experience of how

00:18:11.060 --> 00:18:13.760
pride happens in different
hostile environments

00:18:13.760 --> 00:18:14.880
around the world.

00:18:14.880 --> 00:18:17.750
And so our role is also
to provide some advice

00:18:17.750 --> 00:18:21.470
when is wanted and needed.

00:18:21.470 --> 00:18:27.050
