00:18:35.330 --> 00:18:38.870
We provided this live
reporting service

00:18:38.870 --> 00:18:41.450
from the ground-- which social
media very much offers--

00:18:41.450 --> 00:18:44.554
with Uri providing a live
feed to our supporters,

00:18:44.554 --> 00:18:46.220
and then following
up with lots of media

00:18:46.220 --> 00:18:48.740
work afterwards to really draw
attention to the human rights

00:18:48.740 --> 00:18:51.396
violations that took place.

00:18:51.396 --> 00:18:52.680
