00:24:49.346 --> 00:24:50.220
It's not a narrative.

00:24:50.220 --> 00:24:51.270
It's reality.

00:24:51.270 --> 00:24:54.450
These are homegrown
movements, people working

00:24:54.450 --> 00:24:55.856
for their own liberation.

